ed="T" n="0897c01"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0897c01"/><head><date from-iso="+0907-06-10" key="j20524952058534" to-iso="+0923-12-22">梁</date>泉州<persName key="A008810">智宣</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0897c02"/><persName key="A008810">釋智宣</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000017905">泉州</placeName>人也。壯歲慕法，學<persName key="A001470">義淨</persName>之為<lb
ed="T" n="0897c03"/>人也。輕生誓死，欲遊<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0897sgsz13"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0897sgsz13"/>佛八塔，并<lb
ed="T" n="0897c04"/>求此方未流經法。以唐季結侶渡流沙，所<lb
ed="T" n="0897c05"/>至國土，懷古尋師，好奇徇異，聚<name>梵</name>夾，求<lb
ed="T" n="0897c06"/>舍利。<date key="j20525042052532" notAfter-iso="+0907-07-17" notBefore-iso="+0907-06-19"><name>開平</name>元年五月中</date>達今<placeName key="PL000000023468">東京</placeName>，進辟支佛<lb
ed="T" n="0897c07"/>骨并<name>梵</name>書多羅葉夾經律。<persName key="A008810">宣</persName>壯歲而往，還已<lb
ed="T" n="0897c08"/>衰耄矣。<persName key="A002656">梁太祖</persName>新革唐命，聞<persName key="A008810">宣</persName>迴，大悅，宣<lb
ed="T" n="0897c09"/>賜分物，請譯將歸夾葉。于時干戈，不遑此<lb
ed="T" n="0897c10"/>務也。</p>
